---
layout: base.njk
title: ACM Conference on Agentic and AI Systems | Call for Papers
description: Call for Papers now open for CAIS 2026 — the ACM Conference on Agentic and AI Systems. Submit your research on compound AI architectures, optimization, and deployment. May 26–29, 2026 in San Francisco.
showOpenGraph: true
showJsonLd: true
showSponsorshipCallout: true
---

<!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
<header class="hero">
    <div class="container content">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-12">
                <a href="https://www.acm.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener" aria-label="ACM — Association for Computing Machinery" class="acm-mark-link">
                    <img src="/assets/images/acm_k_flat_pos.png" alt="ACM — Association for Computing Machinery" class="acm-mark" loading="eager" decoding="async" />
                </a>
                <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold mb-3">{{ site.tagline }}</h1>
                <p class="lead mb-4">Submit your research to {{ site.name }} — {{ site.description | lower }}</p>
                <div class="d-flex flex-wrap align-items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                    <span class="fs-5"><i class="bi bi-geo-alt-fill me-1" aria-hidden="true"></i> {{ site.location }}</span>
                    <span class="fs-5"><i class="bi bi-calendar-event me-1" aria-hidden="true"></i> {{ site.dates.display }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="d-flex flex-wrap align-items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                    <span class="fs-4 fw-bold" style="color: var(--cais-accent);"><i class="bi bi-clock me-2" aria-hidden="true"></i>Paper Submission Deadline: {{ site.deadlines.paperSubmission.display }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                    <a href="{{ site.forms.subscribe }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg px-4" style="background:var(--cais-accent); border:none; color:var(--seasalt);">
                        <i class="bi bi-envelope me-2"></i>Subscribe for CFP Updates
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</header>

<!-- ===== WHY CAIS (Pillars) ===== -->
<section id="why" class="py-5 bg-light">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title mb-3">What is CAIS?</h2>
        <p class="lead mb-5">A high-signal forum for rigorous, reproducible research on agentic and AI systems—architectures that shift the Pareto frontier through principled composition of multiple system components, smart inference-time scaling strategies, and systematic verification methods for reliable deployment.</p>
        <div class="row g-4">
            {% for pillar in pillars %}
            {% set pillar = pillar %}
            {% include "pillar-card.njk" %}
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== LEADERSHIP ===== -->
<section id="leadership" class="py-5">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title mb-2">Conference Leadership</h2>
        <p class="lead mb-5">CAIS is guided by leading researchers who defined the compound AI systems paradigm—scholars and practitioners from MIT, Stanford, Google DeepMind, Microsoft Research, and beyond.</p>

        <!-- Steering Committee -->
        <p class="text-uppercase small fw-bold text-muted mb-3" style="letter-spacing: 1px;">Steering Committee</p>
        <div class="row g-4 justify-content-center mb-5">
            {% for member in committee.steering %}
            {% set linkTo = "/pages/committee/#steering" %}
            {% include "committee-thumbnail.njk" %}
            {% endfor %}
        </div>

        <!-- Organizing Committee -->
        <p class="text-uppercase small fw-bold text-muted mb-3" style="letter-spacing: 1px;">Organizing Committee</p>
        <div class="row g-4 justify-content-center">
            {% for member in committee.organizing %}
            {% set linkTo = "/pages/committee/#organizing" %}
            {% include "committee-thumbnail.njk" %}
            {% endfor %}
        </div>

        <div class="text-center mt-4">
            <a href="/pages/committee/" class="btn btn-outline-primary">View Full Committee <i class="bi bi-arrow-right ms-1"></i></a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== PROGRAM PREVIEW ===== -->
<section id="program" class="py-5 bg-light">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title mb-3">Conference Program</h2>
        <p class="lead mb-4">Four days of cutting-edge research presentations, hands-on tutorials, and community building—{{ site.dates.display }} in San Francisco.</p>

        <div class="row g-4">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card card-quiet p-4 h-100">
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-start gap-3 mb-3">
                        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                            <i class="bi bi-file-earmark-text fs-1" style="color:var(--cais-accent);" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="h5 fw-bold mb-2">Research Track</h3>
                            <p class="mb-3">Peer-reviewed papers on architectural patterns, optimization, engineering, and evaluation of agentic AI systems. Includes keynotes, plenaries, and poster sessions.</p>
                            <a href="{{ site.forms.subscribe }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Get CFP Updates</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card card-quiet p-4 h-100">
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-start gap-3 mb-3">
                        <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                            <i class="bi bi-code-slash fs-1" style="color:var(--cais-accent);" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="h5 fw-bold mb-2">Tutorials &amp; Workshops</h3>
                            <p class="mb-3">Deep dives into practical methods and frameworks—DSPy, LangChain, and more tools for building compound AI systems at scale.</p>
                            <a href="/pages/workshops/" class="btn btn-outline-primary">View Workshop Details</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Rigor & Recognition (simplified) -->
        <div class="row g-4 mt-3">
            <div class="col-12">
                <div class="highlight-box p-4">
                    <div class="row align-items-center">
                        <div class="col-lg-8">
                            <h3 class="h5 fw-bold mb-2">Artifact-Centric Review with Reproducibility Badges</h3>
                            <p class="mb-0">CAIS emphasizes open artifacts, transparent evaluation, and benchmarking standards. We adopt ACM's reproducibility badging taxonomy to recognize high-quality, deployable research.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-4 text-lg-end mt-3 mt-lg-0">
                            <a href="{{ site.forms.subscribe }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Subscribe for Details</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

